Incident.Summary: HSI Case # BA07QR22BA0005 - MSP assist with charging suspect as juvenile

IncidentSuppNarrative.NarrativeText: ATTACHMENTS: - HSI Case File - Juvenile Release Form NARRATIVE: On October 28, 2022, HSI Special Agent Rachal Torg requested assistance from TFC Cooke #6272 in regards to a CSAM (child sexual abuse material) investigation. SA Torgs case (Case File #BA07QR22BA0005) involves HSI Baltimore receiving a lead in October of 2021 from a foreign law enforcement agency identifying the target Google email account, stefonwallace17@gmail.com, using an IP address registered to the area of Upper Marlboro, Maryland. On 3/16/2022, HSI executed a residential search warrant of the target address (4504 Cross Country Terrace, Upper Marlboro, MD 20772 in which two cell phones belonging to the suspect, identified as Stefon Amir Wallace (9/17/04 1/M), were seized and forensically examined - later found to contain to CSAM. Due to Wallace being a juvenile (17 years old) at the time of the search warrant and subsequent possession of CSAM, HSI is requesting MSP assistance in charging Wallace as a juvenile. The following portion of this narrative is copied directly from HSI Case File #BA07QR22BA0005: SYNOPSIS Around September and October of 2019, a foreign law enforcement agency was notified of a public hyperlink, which contained photos and videos of the sexual exploitation of children. In October 2021, HSI Baltimore received the lead based on the account user stefonwallace17@gmail.com using an IP address located in Upper Marlboro, Maryland. This report of investigation documents the discovery of child sexual abuse material on seized devices from 4504 Cross Country Terrace, Upper Malboro, Maryland. DETAILS OF INVESTIGATION On March 16, 2022, a search warrant was executed at the residence of 4504 Cross Country Terrace in Upper Marlboro, Maryland. The search warrant included the search of any electronic media located at the site. The seized devices were turned over to Homeland Security Investigations (HSI) Baltimore Computer Forensic Agent (CFA) Joe Mizell. CFA Mizell conducted a forensic analysis of the devices and provided a report of findings to the case agent. A review of the forensic reports by HSI Special Agent (SA) Torg resulted in child sexual abuse material (CSAM) being observed on seized items CELL 1 and CELL 3. Both phones have the phone number 443-554-5591 associated to them. The Apple ID associated with both CELL 1 and CELL 3 is the email account stefonwallace@icloud.com (refer to ROI BA07QR22BA0005-004 for further details). A couple images were observed on CELL 1: Filename: telegram-cloud-photo-size-1-4961091688701471741-y_partial Description: This is a color photograph that depicts a minor female laying on her back on a yellow and white color sofa. The female has one leg lifted and her vagina is exposed. Filename: telegram-cloud-photo-size-1-5105119955229191100-x Description: This is a color photograph that depicts the vagina of a pre-pubescent female, possibly a toddler. The females legs are spread and shows the vagina and part of the lower torso of the female. The minor female is laying on a white sheet or blanket that has red and purple fruit images on it. Several files were observed on CELL 3: Filename: telegram-cloud-document-1-1981181492261552529 Description: A video file, 24 seconds in duration, depicts an adult male orally penetrating a minor females mouth. The minor is wearing a pink sweater and tan colored pants. The adult male has his hand on the minor females head and then attempts to shove his penis deeper into her mouth. The minor female pulls away and pushes herself away from the adult male. Filename: telegram-cloud-document-1-1981181492261552531 Description: A video file, 13 seconds in duration, depicts an adult male rubbing his erect penis on the vaginal area a minor female. The female is on her hands and elbows with her buttocks in the air. The female is watching something on a cellphone, which she is holding in her hands. Filename: telegram-cloud-document-1-1981181492261552533 Description: A video file, 23 seconds in duration, depicts an adult male penetrating a minor female with his penis. The minor female is naked and laying on her back on blue sheets with her legs spread. Filename: telegram-cloud-document-1-4992314558593892848 Description: A video file, 45 seconds in duration, depicts an adult male orally penetrating a minor female with his penis. The camera appears to be hidden behind curtains. The adult male grabs the back of the minor females head with both hands and orally penetrates her mouth. The investigation continues. On 2/8/23 at 1130 hours, TFC Cooke responded to 4504 Cross Country Terrace,Upper Marlboro, MD 20772, and served Wallace with the Juvenile Release Form (signed by Wallaces father, Jeffery Wallace), charging Wallace with three counts of Possession of Child Pornography. The signed Juvenile Release Form and RMS report containing all attachments were sent to the Department of Juvenile Services - Prince Georges County, MD. All events occurred in Prince Georges County, MD. Case closed.
